---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import GalleryLightbox from '../../components/GalleryLightbox.astro';

const title = "Éclat — Web Design for a High-End Jewellery Boutique | Aenea";
const description = "Éclat is a web design by Aenea for a high-end jewellery boutique — a digital extension of luxury, composed with restraint, editorial typography, and curated visuals.";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <Navbar current="work" />

  <main>
    <section class="proj-intro wrap">
      <a href="/work" class="back-link"><span aria-hidden="true">←</span> Selected Work</a>
      <span class="eyebrow proj-cat">Web Design</span>
      <h1 class="proj-title">Éclat</h1>
      <p class="proj-lead">A website for a high-end jewellery boutique — conceived as a digital extension of luxury, where space, typography, and imagery carry the narrative with quiet confidence.</p>
      <div class="proj-meta">
        <div><div class="meta-k">Service</div><div class="meta-v">Web Design</div></div>
        <div><div class="meta-k">Sector</div><div class="meta-v">Luxury &amp; Retail</div></div>
        <div><div class="meta-k">Year</div><div class="meta-v">2025</div></div>
        <div><div class="meta-k">Deliverables</div><div class="meta-v">Web design, Art direction, UI</div></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="case wrap">
      <div class="case-label"><span class="idx">01</span><span class="eyebrow">Overview</span></div>
      <div class="case-body">
        <p>The web design for Éclat Studio is conceived as a digital extension of luxury. Every element is composed to feel polished, intentional, and considered — creating an experience as refined as the jewellery it presents.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="wrap">
      <div class="pair">
        <figure class="ph s6 r43" data-lightbox><img src="/eclat-1.jpg" alt="Éclat website design — homepage for a high-end jewellery boutique, by Aenea" /></figure>
        <figure class="ph s6 r43" data-lightbox><img src="/eclat-2.jpg" alt="Éclat website design — editorial product and layout detail" /></figure>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="case wrap">
      <div class="case-label"><span class="idx">02</span><span class="eyebrow">The Experience</span></div>
      <div class="case-body">
        <p>The layout embraces restraint. Space, typography, and imagery carry the narrative — clean compositions paired with subtle details that elevate the overall feel. Nothing accidental; every interaction measured and deliberate.</p>
        <p>A sense of modern elegance runs throughout. Editorial transitions, refined typography, and curated visuals create a website that commands attention quietly — with confidence and clarity.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="case wrap">
      <div class="case-label"><span class="idx">03</span><span class="eyebrow">Outcome</span></div>
      <div class="case-body">
        <p>The colour palette and visual hierarchy ensure cohesion across every screen — a digital space that mirrors the atmosphere of a boutique interior: immersive, composed, and unmistakably high-end.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="next wrap">
      <a href="/work/jewellery" class="next-link">
        <span class="next-k">Next project</span>
        <span class="next-title">Jewellery Brand <span class="arr" aria-hidden="true">↗</span></span>
        <span class="next-cat">Social Visuals</span>
      </a>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
  <GalleryLightbox />
</Layout>